---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy — SteadyRise">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="legal">
        <p class="updated">Last updated: April 28, 2026</p>

        <p>
          SteadyRise Family Money ("SteadyRise," "we," "us") provides a household
          finance application at <a href="https://app.steadyrise.us">app.steadyrise.us</a>.
          This policy explains what we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have.
        </p>

        <h2>Information we collect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Account information.</strong> Your email address and the authentication metadata required to sign you in.</li>
          <li><strong>Financial data you enter.</strong> The budgets, transactions, accounts, and goals you create or import. This data is stored in an encrypted, managed cloud database.</li>
          <li><strong>Operational logs.</strong> Standard request logs and error reports for reliability and security monitoring.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How we use your information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To operate the SteadyRise application and provide the features you request.</li>
          <li>To authenticate your sessions and protect your family workspace.</li>
          <li>To send transactional email (verification and invitations).</li>
          <li>To diagnose problems, prevent abuse, and improve the product.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What we do not do</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>We do not sell your personal or financial information.</li>
          <li>We do not show third-party advertising.</li>
          <li>We do not share your transactions with marketers or data brokers.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Service providers</h2>
        <p>
          We rely on a small set of vetted third-party service providers to
          operate SteadyRise, including providers of authentication, database
          hosting, transactional email, and content delivery. Each provider
          processes data only as needed to deliver its service to us. A current
          list of subprocessors is available on request.
        </p>

        <h2>Data retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain your data for as long as your account is active. You can request
          deletion of your family workspace at any time by contacting us; backups are
          purged on our standard rotation thereafter.
        </p>

        <h2>Your choices</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Export your data at any time from the Data Management page.</li>
          <li>Request correction or deletion by emailing the address below.</li>
          <li>Add or remove accounts you've created from the Accounts page.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Children</h2>
        <p>SteadyRise is intended for adults managing household finances and is not directed to children under 13.</p>

        <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>We will post any changes to this page and update the "Last updated" date above. Material changes will be communicated by email or through an in-app notice.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:privacy@steadyrise.us">privacy@steadyrise.us</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
